ing that podium.\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1328, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really special thing\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1246}, {\"ngram\": \"that podium\", \"from\": 1256, \"to\": 1267}, {\"ngram\": \"that podium\", \"from\": 1316, \"to\": 1327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it's a step forward, but we are always shooting for gold.\\\"\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1390, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a step\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1343}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1388}]}, {\"sentence\": \"FATHER'S FOOTSTEPS Exactly 32 years ago to the day, David Berkoff won the men's 100 metres backstroke at the Barcelona Games, and his daughter Katharine followed in her father's footsteps in the women's event in Paris.\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1445, \"end\": 1458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Berkoff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Berkoff\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Berkoff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Berkoff\"}, {\"begin\": 1605, \"end\": 1610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999915740549, \"rank\": 8.425937813778148e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"FATHER'S FOOTSTEPS\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1410}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1442}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 100 metres backstroke\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"the Barcelona Games\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1516}, {\"ngram\": \"his daughter\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1534}, {\"ngram\": \"Katharine\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1544}, {\"ngram\": \"her father's footsteps\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1579}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's event\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her father won four Olympic medals in all, and when 23-year-old Berkoff won her first, it was also the 600th medal the U.S. had won in swimming.\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1757, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her father\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1623}, {\"ngram\": \"four Olympic medals\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1647}, {\"ngram\": \"23-year-old Berkoff\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1684}, {\"ngram\": \"the 600th medal\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1727}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1736}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have been dreaming of being at the Olympics for my whole life.\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 1824, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1805}, {\"ngram\": \"my whole life\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I definitely have more goals and I am not quite satisfied yet,\\\" Berkoff told reporters.\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1912, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more goals\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1853}, {\"ngram\": \"Berkoff\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1896}, {\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1911}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When asked if her father had given her any advice, she said: \\\"He's been very supportive, just trying to remind me to stay in my own lane, remember why I am doing what I am doing and just do it for myself and no one else.\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 2134, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her father\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1938}, {\"ngram\": \"any advice\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 1963}, {\"ngram\": \"my own lane\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2050}, {\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2128}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am so grateful they get to be here to watch... just grateful for my parents' support along the way.\\\"\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2239, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my parents' support\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2223}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2237}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australia's Kaylee McKeown defended her backstroke crown while Americans Smith and Berkoff completed the podium.\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2241, \"end\": 2250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9997665114341585, \"rank\": 0.0002117989008155901, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 2253, \"end\": 2267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaylee_McKeown\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kaylee McKeown\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaylee_McKeown\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaylee_McKeown\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her backstroke crown\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2297}, {\"ngram\": \"Americans Smith\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2319}, {\"ngram\": \"Berkoff\", \"from\": 2324, \"to\": 2331}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think other people's performances are completely out of my control and Kaylee is one of one.\", \"from\": 2355, \"to\": 2450, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other people's performances\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2391}, {\"ngram\": \"my control\", \"from\": 2414, \"to\": 2424}, {\"ngram\": \"Kaylee\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She is an absolutely incredible racer and she knows what to do when it matters,\\\" said Smith after claiming her fourth Olympic medal.\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2583, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an absolutely incredible racer\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2488}, {\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2542}, {\"ngram\": \"her fourth Olympic medal\"